{"tid":2390962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安徽中學生因成績不好天台企跳　輔警以自己高考零分相勸成功救人","createTime":"2021-02-02T01:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T03:33:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1d59f8e5093b168026ab72638692df80797563","tid":2390962,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"近日在安徽淮南，一名女中學生因為成績不好欲跳樓輕生，在場的輔警以自己高考零分相勸，成功救下女孩。<br />\n<br />\n事發在1月31日傍晚，當地警方接到報案，某屋苑26樓天台有人企跳。民警趕到現場發現，一名女學生懸坐天台邊緣上，情緒失控正在哭泣。當時情況危急，民警不停安慰女學生並慢慢靠近。得知她因考試成績不好有了輕生想法後，在場一名輔警勸說「我高考考了零分」，引起對方注意，另一名民警則趁機把女學生從天台邊緣抱下來，施救成功。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，欲輕生的女孩是初中三年級學生，下午三時左右就坐在樓頂，一直沒人發現，民警把她送回家時，父母毫不知情。民警將情況告知其家人後，經教育和溝通，女孩對輕生行為感到後悔，父母也表示會反思。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210202/433206230106771456054967.jpeg/Uo57tG2DAtLqicRx-Qc_V_ITAxWlsowx4b-zyuG_s8o?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210202%2F433206230106771456054967.jpeg%2FUo57tG2DAtLqicRx-Qc_V_ITAxWlsowx4b-zyuG_s8o%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=c366a0c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"022bc4bcd0e4dccec4a919ff6dc82fb63bc8a2c0","tid":2390962,"uid":56428,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"零分咪做狗囉。 睇下香港班垃圾"},{"pid":"3abccf8434fa2625fb363c83dc95679a42936702","tid":2390962,"uid":108201,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"屌，我唔想做死黑警先跳樓，你叫我唔好跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4273847be9395d1eeb3534f604dfe9f37c59b413","tid":2390962,"uid":225192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"社會寄生蟲警曱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce35fe2c021408c756d80a88dc67bf3cb1c0aeaa","tid":2390962,"uid":438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"換轉香港應該已經一腳伸佢落街"},{"pid":"5998fb4e0d321530ab8ad068f77b51e972f171f3","tid":2390962,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"所以夜晚都要開工"},{"pid":"9e30d2c2f86e6c5c08900e293ca5e9921ae9e420","tid":2390962,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"初中三年級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc1af8601c70f9f94c9cfd7b6cb8b9c3c7a1152","tid":2390962,"uid":299134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:29:30.000Z","msg":"佢係咪曲線證明緊支那啲公安都係社會垃圾去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c55dfd3bba6255fe9e36e9680e2f24e9d75cd14","tid":2390962,"uid":75868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"鼓勵個女仔大時可以做公安"}]}